  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2067913">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2067913/" class="title-link">难得的一本书。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2067913"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Ste/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2551857-205.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Ste/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">一花集</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-06-10"
      class="main-meta">2009-06-10 14:21:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2067913_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  平实易懂的语言，条理分明、逻辑性强。 邓晓芒将黑格尔的哲学著作一一剖析，中间不乏作者个人强有力的见解。 看法和观点非常吸引人。  因为这本书，开始关注邓晓芒。 

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2067913/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 2没用</span>
